{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-420-2x2-positive-integer-matrix","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Changamoto 420: matriksi 2x2 ya nambari kamili chanya","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Matrica pozitivnih celih brojeva je matrica čiji su svi elementi pozitivni celi brojevi.</p>\n<p>Neke matrice pozitivnih celih brojeva mogu se predstaviti kao kvadrat matrice pozitivnih celih brojeva na dva različita načina. Evo jednog primera:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{pmatrix}\n40 &#x26; 12 \\\\\n48 &#x26; 40\n\\end{pmatrix} =\n{\\begin{pmatrix}\n2 &#x26; 3 \\\\\n12 &#x26; 2\n\\end{pmatrix}}^2 =\n{\\begin{pmatrix}\n6 &#x26; 1 \\\\\n4 &#x26; 6\n\\end{pmatrix}}^2$$</p>\n<p>Neka je $F(N)$ broj matrica 2×2 sa pozitivnim celim brojevima čiji je trag manji od N i koje se mogu predstaviti kao kvadrat matrice pozitivnih celih brojeva na dva različita načina.</p>\n<p>Možemo potvrditi da $F(50) = 7$ i $F(1000) = 1019$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $F({10}^7)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5111000cf542c510023","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302090,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-420-2x2-positive-integer-matrix"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function positiveIntegerMatrix() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npositiveIntegerMatrix();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>positiveIntegerMatrix()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>145159332</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(positiveIntegerMatrix(), 1451593